She looked at him. "I..I can't let the other cubes get into bad 
hands."  She looked at him with the cube. "No, that one is yours. If 
will make you feel better. If not when sick, closer to stop 
functioning then.  It made a bot feel better when the bot stopped 
moving. So, you keep it."  She limped over to him, crying as she 
walked.  "I will go back now."
